╚══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╝

┌─ IDENTITY ──────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│ Binary:    tylluan-nexus (kernel) + tylluan-proxy (gateway) │
│ Port:      :3030 (proxy, fixed) → :303X (kernel, dynamic)  │
│ Config:    tylluan.toml (copy from tylluan.example.toml)    │
│ Auth:      .tylluan-token (bearer, auto-generated, gitignored)│
│ Data:      data/*.db (sqlite) — gitignored, created on boot │
│ License:   MIT                                               │
│ Language:  Rust kernel + Python guilds + React dashboard     │
│ Tests:     cargo test -p tylluan-kernel --lib                │
│ Build:     cargo build -p tylluan-kernel                     │
│ Start:     ./tylluan-mcp.bat (Win) or ./tylluan-mcp.sh (Unix)│
│ Health:    curl http://127.0.0.1:3030/health                 │
│ MCP:       SSE at /sse │ HTTP Streamable at /messages        │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘

