┌─ CRATE MAP ─────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                                                              │
│  Cargo.toml (workspace root)                                 │
│  ├─ tylluan-kernel   THE kernel. All logic lives here.      │
│  ├─ tylluan-proxy    Zero-downtime gateway (:3030)          │
│  ├─ tylluan-common   Shared types: TylluanError, TylluanResult│
│  ├─ tylluan-cli      Interactive REPL (optional)            │
│  ├─ tylluan-link     Federation protocol                    │
│  ├─ tylluan-gui      Tauri desktop app (experimental)       │
│  └─ tylluan-evals    Benchmark suite (LongMemEval, BeamScale)│
│                                                              │
│  95% of changes happen in tylluan-kernel.                    │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘

┌─ KERNEL INTERNALS (crates/tylluan-kernel/src/) ─────────────┐
│                                                              │
│  ENTRY                                                       │
│    main.rs          startup, config load, guild spawn        │
│    config.rs        TylluanConfig, toml parsing, defaults    │
│    setup.rs         database init, model download            │
│                                                              │
│  TRANSPORT (how clients talk to the kernel)                  │
│    transport/http/                                           │
│      mod.rs         axum router, TylluanState, all routes    │
│      auth.rs        bearer token middleware                  │
│      sse.rs         SSE transport for MCP                    │
│      api_v1.rs      40+ REST endpoints                      │
│      api_v1/        per-domain handlers (coloquio, silva,    │
│                     guilds, memory, admin, monitor, etc.)    │
│    transport/server/                                         │
│      mod.rs         TylluanServer — MCP tool handler         │
│      tools.rs       all_tools() → 5 sovereign tools          │
│      handlers.rs    handle_kernel_tool() dispatcher          │
│      handler_do/    tylluan_do pipeline:                     │
│        routing.rs     intent → guild (BM25+anchor scoring)   │
│        embedding.rs   semantic similarity via BGE-M3         │
│        timeout.rs     CPU-safe execution timeouts            │
│      handler_recall.rs   memory search (BM25+vector+rerank) │
│      handler_remember.rs memory write                        │
│      handler_think.rs    graph reasoning                     │
│      handler_graph.rs    direct graph ops                    │
│                                                              │
