│    memory/                                                   │
│      silva/         SilvaDB: graph + vectors + search        │
│        nodes.rs       node CRUD                              │
│        edges.rs       relationship management                │
│        search.rs      hybrid retrieval (BM25+vector+RRF)     │
│        graph.rs       traversal, PPR, path queries           │
│        anchors.rs     routing anchor corpus                  │
│        schema.rs      database migrations                    │
│      hybrid.rs      BM25 + vector fusion                     │
│      coloquio.rs    multi-agent channels                     │
│      mailbox.rs     async agent-to-agent messaging           │
│      identity.rs    agent profiles and context               │
│      idle_lab.rs    background parameter optimization        │
│      dream_cycle.rs background knowledge enrichment          │
│      graph_rag.rs   cluster-aware retrieval                  │
│      ivf_index.rs   IVF vector index                         │
│      louvain.rs     community detection                      │
│                                                              │
│  REGISTRY (guild lifecycle)                                  │
│    registry/                                                 │
