┌─ SAFETY ────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│  ✋ NEVER host=0.0.0.0 + dev_mode=true (unauthenticated RCE)│
│  ✋ NEVER run as root/Administrator                          │
│  ✋ NEVER commit .tylluan-token                              │
│  ✋ NEVER reduce timeouts below defaults (CPU inference)     │
│  ✋ NEVER hardcode guild paths (use catalog.rs)              │
│  See: SECURITY_MODEL in docs/architecture/SECURITY.md       │
│  See: DISCLAIMER.md for operator responsibilities            │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
